It was very convenient to everything we wanted to do, and yet set in a lovely quiet area that had a peaceful and safe ambience.	The atmosphere is warm, modern with a great attention to details.	It is a boutique hotel and has all of the comforts one would expect.	This means it is quiet and relaxing.	This was easily our best stay, so close to all the tourist venues yet at the same time so much quieter and relaxing.	The food was great, and the staff went out of their way to make the meal enjoyable.	Breakfast was more than we expected, with plentiful choices and a sophisticated atmosphere.